Full of pictures, both descriptive and humorous!

8
00:02:25,208 --> 00:02:27,082
Only a penny!

9
00:02:27,916 --> 00:02:32,624
Galanty show!

10
00:02:33,708 --> 00:02:36,582
Pictures of every description in colour.

11
00:02:40,166 --> 00:02:45,915
See John Guildford make his famous ride,
and only one penny!

12
00:02:50,458 --> 00:02:52,540
lf you haven't got a penny,

13
